    | NAMESPACE
    | NEW
    | NOTNULL
    | NOT    // C# 9 patterns
    | NULL_
    | OBJECT
    | OPERATOR
    | OR     // C# 9 patterns
    | OUT
    | OVERRIDE
    | PARAMS
    | PRIVATE
    | PROTECTED
    | PUBLIC
    | READONLY
    | REF
